Package: tinyexpect
Title: Additional Expecation Predicates for the 'tinytest' Testing Framework
Version: 0.0.0.9010
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        given = "Paul",
        family = "Hoffman",
        email = "hoff0792@alumni.umn.edu",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7693-8957")
    )
    )
Description: Ports of 'testthat' expectation predicates to the 'tinytest'
    testing framework. These ports allow easier transitioning from 'testthat'
    to 'tinytest' as well as provide more explicit expectation predicates for
    'tinytest' users.
